tps:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-I0","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32317,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/no-true-faith-arguing-in-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":2728,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Iman: No true faith until he stops arguing in religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the servant does not entirely have faith until he abandons lying even while joking, and he abandons arguing even if he is truthful.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8566 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":110,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/11\/13\/not-allowed-prank-scare\/","url_meta":{"origin":2728,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Pranks: Not allowed to scare another Muslim on purpose","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Layla reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is not lawful for a Muslim to frighten another Muslim.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 5004 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40579,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/laughing-fart-jokes\/","url_meta":{"origin":2728,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mockery: Prohibition of laughing at someone\u2019s farts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from laughing at someone who passes wind. Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 9433 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0646\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0649 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0636\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0650\u0643\u0650 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0636\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0629\u0650 9433 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u062c\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0648\u0633\u0637\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33612,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/jokes-nikah-talaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":2728,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jokes: Not allowed to play about divorce, freedom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadallah ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is not permissible to jest about three matters: divorce, marriage, and emancipation.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 780 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":105,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/11\/08\/warning-lies-jokes\/","url_meta":{"origin":2728,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Joking: Warning not to tell a lie, even as a joke","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'awiyyah ibn Haydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWoe to one who tells lies to make people laugh. Woe to him! Woe to him!\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4990 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u0639\u0627\u0648\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u064a\u062f\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u